  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of P-3073 Nail Solution in the Treatment of Nails Affected by Psoriasis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Vehicle-controlled, Parallel Group Trial to Assess the Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of P-3073 for Topical Treatment of Nail Psoriasis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
