  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm the clinical efficacy and the safety of P-3073 in
      patients affected by isolated psoriatic nail(s) and/or those with psoriatic nails and
      concomitant mild to moderate plaque psoriasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
